snippet.title: Ice Age 3: Dawn of the Dinosaurs - Gameplay [Java Game]
snippet.description:
Ice Age 3: Dawn of the Dinosaurs it was a java game developed by Glu Mobile and released in 2009

Our beloved sub-zero heroes return for an action-packed rescue mission in Ice Age: Dawn of the Dinosaurs. Sid has disappeared into a strange world beneath the Ice Age and needs to escape the dinosaurs to find his friends. Follow the adventure in another round of prehistoric fun.

Link to the game: http://dedomil.net/games/1108/screen/8
Version used in video - K800i (240x320)
